 restaurants in Arequipa.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1436955974"><a href="/south-america/peru/articles/the-10-best-seafood-restaurants-in-lima/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3705191-miraflores.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/south-america/peru/articles/the-10-best-seafood-restaurants-in-lima/"><h3>The 10 Best Seafood Restaurants in Lima</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Scoping out Lima's top 10 seafood restaurants.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1436554305"><a href="/south-america/peru/articles/the-best-peruvian-restaurants-in-cusco/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3702029-14365103834fea5d7f330a43ffa3dab83df6a00dca.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/south-america/peru/articles/the-best-peruvian-restaurants-in-cusco/"><h3>The Best Peruvian Restaurants in Cusco</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Cusco is one of the most popular destinations in Peru. Some of their most popular attractions are the Plaza de Armas and the nearby Machu Picchu. After a long day of sight-seeing, unwind with some traditional Peruvian food. Below we have listed some of our favorite Peruvian restaurants in Cusco.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1435336788"><a href="/south-america/peru/articles/the-best-street-food-in-cusco/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3694377-1435296987605273dde1d54bb0b53f793309607a0b.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/south-america/peru/articles/the-best-street-food-in-cusco/"><h3>The Best Street Food in Cusco</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Street food is an authentic, inexpensive way to din